channel.title: Npc spawn list?
channel.description:
Hello everyone, yes i'm a bit new here :P
But onto the question. I was wondering if anyone knew where i could get the entire npc spawn. Like for all of rs. I'm sure i remember seeing it somewhere. Like where all the npcs are spawned in their correct spots?
Maybe this is asking too much but if anybody knows where i could get it for my server, it would be greatly appreciated!
Thanks.
